text: Dimitar Krastanov () (born 31 January 1994) is a Bulgarian modern pentathlete. He competed at the 2016 Summer Olympics in Rio de Janeiro, in the men's event. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1994 births Category:Living people Category:Bulgarian male modern pentathletes Category:Olympic modern pentathletes of Bulgaria Category:Modern pentathletes at the 2016 Summer Olympics
